          <li>Log in to the school's app and go to the "Pay Fees" section.</li>
          <li>Select "Departmental Payment Fees".</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <i class="fas fa-list-check"></i>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Step 2: Checking Fees Requirements</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Review tuition, exam, and other fees.</li>
          <li>Verify the total amount to be paid.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <i class="fas fa-pencil-alt"></i>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Step 3: Proceeding to Payment</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Return to the "Pay Fees" section.</li>
          <li>Acknowledge the amount to be paid.</li>
          <li>Select your department and enter the payment amount.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Step 4: Payment Processing</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Ensure all information entered is accurate.</li>
          <li>Tap "Start to Process" to begin.</li>
          <li>System redirects you to the Bursar/Registrar's WhatsApp for confirmation.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Step 5: Confirmation and Payment</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Confirm your payment with the Bursar or Registrar.</li>
          <li>Follow their instructions to complete the payment.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

